buryFestival-The-Common-Temple-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/GlastonburyFestival-The-Common-Temple-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/GlastonburyFestival-The-Common-Temple-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/GlastonburyFestival-The-Common-Temple-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/glastonbury-2024">格拉斯顿伯里音乐节</a>已公布 The Common 2024 年完整演出阵容 - 您可以在下面查看。</p><p>传奇的 Worthy Farm 活动将于下个月回归，届时将有<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dua-lipa">Dua Lipa</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/coldplay">Coldplay</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sza">SZA</a>以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/shania-twain">Shania Twain</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lcd-soundsystem">LCD Soundsystem</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/little-simz">Little Simz</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-national">The National 等</a>乐队的头条新闻。</p><ul><li><strong>了解更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-line-up-set-times-stage-splits-3749871">格拉斯顿伯里音乐节 2024：查看迄今为止的完整阵容和舞台划分</a></strong></li></ul><p>继三月份<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-line-up-revealed-who-playing-poster-3600775">确认第一波演出</a>后，组织者一直在为音乐节的许多区域和舞台投放单独的海报，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-english-teacher-sprints-bob-vylan-and-lottery-winners-among-acts-for-left-field-line-up-3752348">Left Field</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-announce-stacked-line-up-for-woodsies-area-3752059">Woodsies</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/faithless-fatboy-slim-camelphat-groove-armada-lead-glastonbury-2024-glade-area-line-up-3749471">The Glade</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-adds-more-names-to-line-up-acoustic-stage-3616963">Acoustic Stage</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-romy-kelly-lee-owens-shygirl-and-more-added-to-glastonbury-as-silver-hayes-line-up-revealed-3751900">Silver Hayes</a> 。</p><p>今天（5 月 3 日）格拉斯顿伯里公布了 The Common 的另一份名单，其中包括 The Temple、Rum Shack 和 Mez Yard 等场馆。</p><p> “[The Common]是一个诞生于我们集体想象力、梦想和建筑的空间，我们都是其中的一部分，”一份声明写道。 “它来自于在我们的世界、土地和心中重新夺回空间的历史，成为我们自己，而不是我们被告知的那样，按照我们自己的节奏跳舞。这是他们 2024 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节的阵容。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kae-tempest">Kae Tempest</a>将参加“寺庙起义：集体解放的声音力量”，该活动“探索音乐如何超越娱乐，成为革命和解放的催化剂”。</p><p>名单上的其他乐队还有<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/katy-b">Katy B</a> 、A Guy Called Gerald、Katalyst、4am Kru、Manni Dee、Jessica Wilde、Marc Stylus、Paul&#39;s Mobile Disco、Oh Annie Oh、Natty Speaks、GotSome 和 Coco Em。</p><p>请参阅下面 The Common 官方海报上的完整行为列表，并在其 <a href="https://www.glastonburyfestivals.co.uk/areas/the-common/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">区域页面</a>上找到更多信息。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C6gCEAqKbcS/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/x